<Paintings>
  <Text 310 310 20 #000000 0 "AM Modulator">
  <Text 310 360 11 #000000 0 "Opamp gain depends on JFET resistance which is modulated by the modulating signal.\n\n\nVsignal is the modulating 10kHz signal">
  <Text 350 420 11 #000000 0 "Power sources">
  <Text 320 470 11 #000000 0 "Power sources">
  <Text 310 820 11 #000000 0 "Modulated signal spectrum (OUT) is Fc-Fm, Fc+Fm.\nFm max frequency modulating signal\nFc carrier wave frequency\nPeaks can be seen in the FT\nUse gaussian window function">
  <Text 310 1880 11 #000000 0 "Modulated signal spectrum (OUT) is Fc-Fm, Fc+Fm.\nFm max frequency modulating signal\nFc carrier wave frequency\nPeaks can be seen in the FT\nUse gaussian window function">
  <Text 310 2040 11 #000000 0 "Audio signal to be tested in the place of Vsignal. \nUsing a 200kHz carrier, the spectrum is at 200-5 and 200+5 kHz">
  <Text 860 2310 11 #000000 90 "Audio">
</Paintings>
